g with features like app connectivity, remote control, integrated lighting, and an ultra-silent motor.","feature_1":"Up to 5 Years Premium Warranty","feature_2":"Free Delivery to Metro Areas","feature_3":"","feature_4":"","feature_5":"","feature_6":"","feature_7":"","feature_8":"","sub_feature_1":"Smart Home App Control","sub_feature_2":"One-Touch Lifting","sub_feature_3":"Easy Install and Usage","sub_feature_4":"Clean, dry, and flat clothes!","sub_feature_5":"","sub_feature_6":"","whatsapp_url":"","whatsapp_text":"Need Help? Whatsapp Us"}},"product_tabs_hero_kpU4DN":{"type":"product-tabs-hero","name":"Product Tabs + Hero","settings":{"tab_1_label":"Description","tab_2_label":"Additional information","tab_3_label":"Reviews (134)","hero_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_Mar_30_2026_05_25_35_PM.png","hero_subtitle":"Nuracom Aero","hero_heading":"Australia's Best Automated Laundry Rack","hero_text_color":"#ffffff","overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":30,"description_content":"","additional_content":"","spec_1_label":"Dimensions","spec_1_value":"1500mm x 380mm x 100mm","spec_2_label":"Weight","spec_2_value":"25kg","spec_3_label":"Material","spec_3_value":"Aluminium Alloy","spec_4_label":"Warranty","spec_4_value":"5 Years","spec_5_label":"","spec_5_value":"","spec_6_label":"","spec_6_value":"","spec_7_label":"","spec_7_value":"","spec_8_label":"","spec_8_value":"","reviews_content":"<p>\"I can't go back to a normal dryer or clothes line now... Its so good!\"<\/p>"}},"product_details_grid_tJgndW":{"type":"product-details-grid","blocks":{"promise_item_3gBkUn":{"type":"promise_item","settings":{"title":"5 Year Warranty","subtitle":"The best after-sales care"}},"promise_item_4igiLg":{"type":"promise_item","settings":{"title":"Great Value & Easy Install","subtitle":"Free Delivery & Install Guidance"}},"promise_item_DQtb98":{"type":"promise_item","settings":{"title":"Transparent Prices & Great Quality","subtitle":"No middleman or markup fees, only fantastic materials."}}},"block_order":["promise_item_3gBkUn","promise_item_4igiLg","promise_item_DQtb98"],"name":"Product Details Grid","settings":{"heading":"A New Benchmark in Modern Design and Innovation.","description":"<p>Nuracom is a modern electric laundry rack built for homes that want smarter drying, better hygiene, and a cleaner everyday routine. Designed to combine convenience with performance, it features telescopic poles to give you flexible hanging space without taking over the room. It’s made for households that want laundry to feel faster, easier, and more efficient.<\/p>","promise_heading":"The Nuracom Satisfaction Guarantee.","media_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Nuracom_Breeze_product_image_transparent_7fe5d93a-044e-4167-8933-5467fbd77240.png","video_url":"","specs_heading":"Technical Specifications","specs_content":"<p><strong>Model:<\/strong> Nuracom Breeze <br\/><strong>Telescopic Pole Range:<\/strong> <strong>110–180 cm<br\/>Main Host Size: 1000 × 330 × 80 mm<br\/>Lifting Height:<\/strong> 160–1200 mm<br\/><strong>Load Capacity:<\/strong> 35kg<br\/><strong>Material:<\/strong> Top Grade Aluminium Alloy<br\/><strong>Functions:<\/strong> Lighting + Drying + Lifting<br\/><strong>Safety Features:<\/strong> Obstruction Sensor<br\/><strong>Motor:<\/strong> Ultra-silent motor<br\/><strong>Control:<\/strong> Remote Control + One-touch Lifting<br\/><strong>Smart Home App:<\/strong> Yes (Tuya App)<br\/><strong>Voice Control Module:<\/strong> No, available in Aero & Stratos<br\/><strong>Ioniser Module:<\/strong> No, available in Stratos only<br\/><strong>LED Light:<\/strong> Single lighting mode<br\/><strong>Power Plug:<\/strong> Australian flat 3 pin plug<br\/><strong>Rated Power:<\/strong> 800W<br\/><strong>Warranty:<\/strong> 5-year motor warranty, 2-year parts, 1-year unit warranty<br\/><br\/><\/p><p><\/p>","bg_color":"#fffbf7","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40}},"control_modes_HBrDFj":{"type":"control-modes","blocks":{"mode_card_qJfeUi":{"type":"mode_card","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon_emoji":"","title":"Voice Control","description":"Take convenience to the next level with intelligent voice control! With a quick voice command, you can operate the light, blower, heater, and other core features without lifting a finger."}},"mode_card_wzHhRK":{"type":"mode_card","settings":{"icon_emoji":"","title":"Remote Control","description":"Enjoy easy control from a distance with the included remote, offering reliable operation within a 30-metre range. Change settings effortlessly from wherever you’re most comfortable."}},"mode_card_wJRiap":{"type":"mode_card","settings":{"icon_emoji":"","title":"Mobile App Control","description":"Manage your drying environment with ease by controlling the light, blower, and heater, while scheduling run times for greater energy efficiency. Wherever you are, your laundry system stays within reach."}},"mode_card_ryPnVH":{"type":"mode_card","disabled":true,"settings":{"icon_emoji":"","title":"Designed for Aussie Homes","description":"Engineered for simple installation in Aussie homes, NuraCom is designed to be mounted to suitable ceiling trusses, creating a secure and practical setup. This allows for a more efficient installation process."}}},"block_order":["mode_card_qJfeUi","mode_card_wzHhRK","mode_card_wJRiap","mode_card_ryPnVH"],"name":"Control Modes","settings":{"heading":"2 Modes Of Control At Your Fingertips","subtitle":"Nuracom Breeze puts smart control at your fingertips, allowing you to manage key functions easily from the convenience of your smartphone.","bg_color":"#fffbf7","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"feature_showcase_UYEW4F":{"type":"feature-showcase","blocks":{"feature_row_qPngRA":{"type":"feature_row","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"A True Sense of Cleanliness","description":"<p>NuraCom Aero uses advanced UV light technology designed to support a cleaner, more hygienic drying experience. By helping reduce lingering bacteria on garments during the drying process, it adds an extra layer of confidence to your everyday laundry routine. The result is clothing that feels fresher, cleaner, and better cared for.<\/p>","callout_title":"with Excellent Safety Measures","callout_text":"To support safe everyday use, the system includes an inbuilt safety mechanism that automatically switches off the UV light when human presence is detected in the area."}}},"block_order":["feature_row_qPngRA"],"name":"Feature Showcase","settings":{"bg_color":"#fffbf7","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"mosaic_feature_gy4gH8":{"type":"mosaic-feature","name":"Mosaic Feature","settings":{"heading":"Easy Lifting with One Touch","subtitle":"With Nuracom Breeze, drying clothes becomes a simpler, more seamless part of your everyday routine.","r1_image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2026-04-09_20-54-39.00_00_00_02.Still007.png","r1_text":"<p>The Breeze is the most lightweight of the models, allowing easy install, quick drying, and guaranteed time savings.<\/p>","r1_image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2026-04-09_20-54-39.00_00_00_06.Still008.png","r2_text_1":"<p>Designed for smooth and effortless operation, Nuracom Breeze features a scissor-arm lifting frame that extends and retracts with ease, making it an ideal solution for busy households with frequent laundry loads.<\/p>","r2_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Hand_lifting_curtain_track_in_modern_home.png","r2_text_2":"<p>With Nuracom Breeze, getting started is effortless. Once clothes are hung, a light upward push raises the rack and begins the drying process, creating a smoother and more intuitive laundry experience.<\/p>","bg_color":"#fffbf7","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"fullwidth_overlay_banner_XBmtee":{"type":"fullwidth-overlay-banner","name":"Full-Width Overlay Banner","settings":{"heading":"Economy++ Energy Savings","description":"<p>To support both safety and energy-conscious performance, NuraCom Breeze includes an automatic shut-off function that powers the system down after two hours of operation. It’s a smart feature designed to reduce unnecessary energy use while giving you added peace of mind.<br\/>This alone saves tons on your electricty bill!<\/p>","btn_label":"","btn_url":"","btn_bg_color":"#866653","btn_text_color":"#ffffff","min_height":400,"overlay_color":"#7a0505","overlay_opacity":45,"text_color":"#ffffff"}},"dark_light_split_wb9tYK":{"type":"dark-light-split","name":"Dark + Light Split","settings":{"dark_heading":"Quieter than a mouse.","dark_description":"<p>Because comfort matters, NuraCom Aero is designed to operate with minimal noise for a more peaceful home environment. Its upgraded DC motor is also engineered to reduce ongoing wear, helping deliver smoother operation and lasting reliability over time.<\/p>","dark_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ultrasilent_motors2.png","dark_bg_color":"#1a1a1a","dark_text_color":"#fffbf7","light_heading":"Custom to the last feature.","light_description":"<p>Enjoy greater control over your laundry space with superb lighting built into the Nuracom Breeze. <br\/>It’s a practical feature that makes laundry more comfortable at any time of day, while also allowing the unit to function as a sleek and useful light source for the room.<\/p>","light_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_1393.jpg","light_bg_color":"#fffbf7"}},"product_recommendations_qggXJq":{"type":"product-recommendations","blocks":{"text_cbcgyb":{"type":"text","name":"t:names.header","settings":{"text":"<h3>You may also like <\/h3>","width":"fit-content","max_width":"normal","alignment":"left","type_preset":"h4","font":"var(--font-primary--family)","font_size":"","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0},"blocks":{}},"static-product-card":{"type":"_product-card","name":"t:names.product_card","static":true,"settings":{"product_card_ga